<polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NV.IND.MANF.ZS?locations=IN">世界银行</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>然而，当你观察印度的就业情况时，就会发现制造业主导着服务业： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg" width="643" height="428.6666666666667" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:450,&quot;width&quot;:675,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:643,&quot;bytes&quot;:57014,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb7ed9426-37fb-4785-89e1-98bb2e0d8670_675x450.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://x.com/Trinhnomics/status/1800383169352654968">@Trinhnomics</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>现在，这两件事并不<em>一定</em>矛盾——印度的服务业可能比制造业生产力高得多——但这肯定是一个需要解释的差异。因此，当我注意到<a href="https://www.livemint.com/Opinion/F6IsyPD0eTcSEM5Fb0ZAYK/Indias-GDP-Deflating-the-right-way.html">印度实际上存在一场关于如何衡量制造业的大争论</a>时，我非常感兴趣。这是2017年的：</p><blockquote><p>关于中央统计局 (CSO) 提出的国内生产总值 (GDP) 增长数字的无休止的争论一直在进行……有两种方法可以将当前价格 GVA（增加值总额）数字缩减为其不变价格等值：单放气和双放气。虽然单一通缩方法主张对当前价格的输入和输出使用一次性系列代理通货紧缩指数，但双通货紧缩方法涉及对输出和输入使用不同的通货紧缩指数，以获得按不变价格计算的产出和 GVA 值……</p><p> CSO 一直混合使用这两种方法。对于农业、采矿业和采石业以外的部门，一直采用单一通货紧缩方法。这种方法是有争议的，因为 GVA 的八个关键组成部分及其子组成部分没有以类似的方式处理，从而妨碍了跨部门进展的比较。</p></blockquote><p>通过这一调整，Jyoti Sharma <a href="https://www.ideasforindia.in/topics/poverty-inequality/india-s-gdp-deflating-the-right-way.html">发现</a>印度制造业在 2015-16 年的增长速度几乎是官方数据显示的三倍，而服务业增长则要慢得多。这导致<a href="https://x.com/Tsitati_George/status/1802767324430139784">一些印度专家认为</a>，印度最近的增长实际上是制造业主导的，而不是服务业主导的。</p><p>这是一个非常重要的问题！<a href="https://x.com/Trinhnomics/status/1800380776229621935">一些人认为</a>，印度应该发挥自身优势，更多地关注服务业，而另一些人则认为，印度应该重点弥补制造业的弱点。但如果印度的制造业实际上比任何人意识到的要多得多，并且这一点被一种以不同方式衡量服务业价格和制造业价格的统计怪癖所掩盖，那么所有这些重大的重大辩论都需要改变。</p><p>第二个数据谜团涉及欧盟和美国之间的增长差距这张图表一直在流传，显示自2008年金融危机以来欧元区和美国生产率增长率存在巨大差异： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef8884c-d19f-4a64-83d3-4306eb4c9e6d_680x616.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef8884c-d19f-4a64-83d3-4306eb4c9e6d_680x616.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef8884c-d19f-4a64-83d3-4306eb4c9e6d_680x616.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit