China's demographics will be fine through mid-centuryThere is no imminent crisis. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/chinas-demgraphics-will-be-fine https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/chinas-demgraphics-will-be-fineNoah Smith Thu, 20 Jun 2024 05:05:21 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg" width="913" height="535" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:535,&quot;width&quot;:913,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:96162,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">照片由<a href="https://unsplash.com/@lanlinn?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Lan Lin</a>在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/a-group-of-people-walking-through-a-field-of-flowers-NuW6GdllbU8?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上拍摄</figcaption></figure></div><p>在讨论中国经济时，人口问题经常被提及。 2022年，中国人口 <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/18/china/china-population-drop-explainer-intl-hnk/index.html">开始减少</a>（巧合的是，印度人口<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/china-reacts-india-overtake-worlds-most-populous-country-economy-rcna80581">超过了中国</a>）。该国的生育率几十年前就已经低于更替水平， <a href="https://www.wsj.com/world/china/chinas-fertility-rate-dropped-sharply-study-shows-e97e647f">最近又再次下降，仅为1.09</a> ，是世界上生育率最低的国家之一，甚至低于日本。</p><p>这引发了中国国内人士和外国观察人士对中国经济未来的许多担忧。例如， <a href="https://www.wsj.com/world/china/chinas-fertility-rate-dropped-sharply-study-shows-e97e647f">这是《华尔街日报》中的一句话</a>：</p><blockquote><p> “随着人口达到顶峰，中国正在显现出日本化的迹象，”国家支持的智库国家金融与发展研究院副院长尹建峰在六月发表的一篇文章中写道。尹敦促中国政府在儿童抚养和教育方面投入更多资金，以避免重蹈日本数十年停滞不前的命运。</p></blockquote><p>这是<a href="https://www.economist.com/china/2024/04/09/chinas-high-stakes-struggle-to-defy-demographic-disaster">《经济学人》</a> ：</p><blockquote><p>中国经济也因此面临萎缩的风险。随着巨大的护理负担即将来临，政府预感到一场灾难即将来临……中国正在未富先老。 2008年，当日本人口开始下降时，按今天的美元计算，其人均GDP已约为47,500美元。中国的只要21,000美元。随着越来越多的资金用于保护老年人，可供工薪一代消费或投资的资金就会减少。</p></blockquote><p>这是我能在<a href="https://theconversation.com/chinas-doom-loop-a-dramatically-smaller-and-older-population-could-create-a-devastating-global-slowdown-221554">《对话》</a>中找到的最可怕的帖子：</p><blockquote><p>人口转移可能导致<a href="https://www.investopedia.com/doom-loop-6748009">“末日循环”</a> ……随着生产率下降开始影响特定部门的生产，中国可能被迫增加进口以满足这些行业的需求……这可能会严重影响创新和创业精神，进而进一步降低生产率。<a href="https://www.nber.org/system/files/working_papers/w26651/w26651.pdf">新想法</a>……推动经济增长。劳动力规模影响创新，因为随着就业人数的减少，新创意的库变得更窄……如果人口增长变为<a href="https://www.nber.org/system/files/working_papers/w26651/w26651.pdf">负数或降至零</a>，那么这些创意背后的知识就会停滞不前。此外，有证据表明，一个人的创新活动和科学产出的<a href="https://www.cato.org/cato-journal/spring/summer-2018/demographics-their-implications-economy-policy#demographic-implications-for-economic-growth">顶峰</a>出现在30岁和40岁左右……因此，当前的人口趋势可能会抑制中国的技术进步和创新……同时， <a href="https://www.econbiz.de/Record/entrepreneurship-and-demographics-liang-james/10013112441">研究</a>表明创业可能会受到人口老龄化的负面影响，因为年轻人的比例与创业活动呈正相关。这阻碍了经济的活力并导致经济增长放缓。</p></blockquote><p>现在，我确实<em>认为</em><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/chinese-demography">从长远来看这对中国来说是一个问题</a>。事实上，中国在这方面绝非独一无二——每个发达国家都在迅速老龄化，大多数发展中国家也不甘落后。</p><p>人口老龄化确实会<em>带来</em>负面影响。我在这篇文章中写了这些问题： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;f6b7772c-4077-458e-93c0-4fd566508326&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;The problem with population growth projections is that they naturally follow an exponential curve. When &#8220;like begets like&#8221; &#8212; when the number of kids is just proportional to how many people are currently alive to have kids &#8212; you get a function that either explodes to infinity or decays to zero as time goes on. So no matter what the fertility rate is, humanity is&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Humanity is going to shrink&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-08-22T21:43:59.679Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F832a104e-51e3-4585-8548-b5659024107e_919x690.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/humanity-is-going-to-shrink&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:136311679,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:263,&quot;comment_count&quot;:201,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}"></div><p>事实上，人口减少并不是真正的问题——而是<em>老龄化</em>。老年抚养比的上升确实给劳动人民带来了巨大的经济负担，而劳动力老龄化可能确实会降低创新和生产率的增长。尽管实现了自动化，但情况确实如此。一个老年人头重脚轻的世界将是一个全世界年轻人都必须更加努力工作的世界。</p><p>但从短期来看，我认为对中国人口结构的灾难性描述有些过头了。拼命寻找理由来消除中国竞争威胁的美国人可能会试图抓住中国低生育率的机会。但中国的经济实力不会因人口老龄化而“崩溃”或消失；事实上，正如我将解释的那样，直到本世纪下半叶，它可能不会因老化而出现严重问题。</p><p>与此同时，更大的危险是，中国领导人将对该国的人口结构感到恐慌，并采取非常鲁莽的行动。我的前彭博同事哈尔·布兰兹 (Hal Brands) <a href="https://democracyparadox.com/2023/07/11/hal-brands-thinks-china-is-a-declining-power-heres-why-thats-a-problem/">认为</a>，中国可能会在未来几年内在亚洲发动战争，因为担心再等下去，其实力就会下降——类似于 1914 年德国仓促发动战争的方式，因为其领导人相信自己的观点。窗户正在消失。正如我将证明的那样，这种担心是没有根据的。但这并不是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/what-if-xi-jinping-isnt-that-competent">习近平犯下的第一个鲁莽错误</a>。</p><p>因此，了解中国人口状况的非紧迫性对美国人和中国人民都有好处。</p><h4>中国即将出现婴儿潮</h4><p>中国人口结构没有出现灾难性的第一个也是最重要的原因是，他们拥有一大批目前年龄在5至15岁的年轻人，这将在未来几年缓解人口压力。</p><p>维基百科有一个很好的中国<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aging_of_China#/media/File:China_population_pyramid_from_2023_to_2100.gif">人口金字塔动画</a>，数据来自联合国的预测。这是 2024 年金字塔的样子。我在图表上标注了世代标签，大致对应于美国的类似世代： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg" width="690" height="565.9642857142857" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:689,&quot;width&quot;:840,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:690,&quot;bytes&quot;:137350,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">改编自 Tweedle -<a href="http://CC BY-SA 4.0, https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=127018432">自己的作品</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>正如你所看到的，中国目前的年轻工作一代——Zoomers——是一个小一代。但比这更年轻的一代——目前年龄在 5 到 15 岁的 Alpha 一代——比 Zoomers 更大。</p><p>中国的阿尔法时期并不是传统意义上的真正的“婴儿潮”——5到15年前生育率并没有出现激增。相反，阿尔法一代是<em>人口统计上千禧一代的呼应</em>，而千禧一代本身就是中国极其庞大的婴儿潮一代的呼应。美国在婴儿潮时期的生育率为 3.5； <a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/fertility-rate-with-projections?time=earliest..2021&amp;country=~CHN">中国的已经超过6了</a>。中国有很多阿尔法一代，只是因为当时有大量的婴儿潮一代。</p><p>无论如何，随着阿尔法人在未来十年达到工作年龄，他们将稳定中国的人口结构。中国的劳动年龄人口实际上预计在未来几年会<em>增加</em>，然后开始缓慢下降： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6ae66d-9423-47be-acc0-07030f519286_1020x812.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6ae66d-9423-47be-acc0-07030f519286_1020x812.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6ae66d-9423-47be-acc0-07030f519286_1020x812.jp