a-has-become-a-scientific-superpower">一个关于中国科学兴起的好故事</a>。就“高影响力”（即高度引用）出版物而言，中国已经超越了美国和欧洲： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg" width="684" height="350.015625" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:393,&quot;width&quot;:768,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:684,&quot;bytes&quot;:78159,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.economist.com/science-and-technology/2024/06/12/china-has-become-a-scientific-superpower">经济学家</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>现在，这些数字必须用一粒盐处理。通过查看数量的其他论文来衡量论文的影响可能是对真实影响的有偏见的衡量标准 - 您可以拥有一群研究人员，他们互相互相援引，从而使度量标准夸大。 Qiu，Steinwender和Azoulay<a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w32468">最近有一篇论文</a>，他们认为这种现象在中国尤为普遍：</p><blockquote><p>我们重点介绍了引用中的一种新颖的偏见来源，这与跨国比较特别相关：家庭偏见，即研究人员倾向于过度引用自己国家的研究人员的趋势……</p><p>我们发现，中国展现出迄今为止所有国家中最大的家庭偏见。这不是最近的现象。尽管过去二十年来中国的家庭偏见一直在稳步增长，但中国的引用已经在2000年（我们的观察期开始）上偏见。此外，中国的家庭偏见并不是由任何特定研究领域驱动的。相反，中国在20个广泛的科学领域中的18个中表现出最大的家庭偏见……</p><p>最后，我们发现家庭偏见夸大了中国在科学上的兴起。尽管中国在原始引用方面排名第二，但一旦我们使用偏见的度量，它又落后于美国，英国和德国的第四位。如果人们认为家庭引用特别容易反映政治或战略考虑，而不是承认科学家对他们选择引用的文章中所包含的思想，则可以看作是特别有用的内容。</p></blockquote><p>研究人员基本上只是通过控制一个国家的规模来识别“家庭偏见”。他们对家庭偏见的度量仍然显示出明显的规模依赖性，欧洲小国家处于规模的底端，大国最高国家。因此，我确实想知道它们是否正确控制了尺寸。但是中国在包括印度在内的所有其他肯定都肯定会脱颖而出： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg" width="837" height="608" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:608,&quot;width&quot;:837,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:122202,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w32468">Qiu等。 (2024)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>因此，尽管我认为作者的结论是，英国在高影响力科学方面仍在中国领先，但就中国研究人员互相援引彼此而言，确实确实在这里发生了一些事情。</p><p>您可以解释这两种不同的方式。 <a href="https://blogs.lse.ac.uk/impactofsocialsciences/2023/03/29/standing-on-the-shoulders-of-chinese-scientific-giants-evidence-for-a-citation-discount-for-chinese-researchers/">一种可能性</a>是，中国科学比中国以外的人意识到的高质量要高得多，由于语言障碍，非中国言论者未能引用这些高质量的中国论文。 Qiu等人的替代解释。建议 - 中国政府告诉该国的研究人员出去撰写引用大量引用的论文，研究人员基本上做出了回应，以建立隐式或明确的<a href="https://scienceintegritydigest.com/2022/03/23/citation-statistics-and-citation-rings/">引用戒指</a>。当然，这可能是这两个解释的一定组合。</p><p> （更新：在评论中，对作者通货膨胀<a href="https://psycnet.apa.org/buy/2024-30105-001">进行研究</a>并与中国科学家合作的研究的Zhicheng Lin<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/is-the-west-falling-behind-in-science/comment/59185842">提出了另一种解释</a>。他认为，中国研究人员的压力比其他地方的研究人员更大，以引用自己部门的高级研究人员.)</p><p>同样，尚不清楚中国在科学方面超过了发达国家。正如《经济学人》文章所表明的那样，自1990年代以来，中国的研发支出迅速增长： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c92441d-0d9c-4dcf-bb3c-ca39a2afa0a1_384x444.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c92441d-0d9c-4dcf-bb3c-ca39a2afa0a1_384x444.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c92441d-0d9c-4dcf-bb3c-ca39a2afa0a1_384x444.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c92441d-0d9c-4dcf-bb3c-ca39a2afa0a1_384x444.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fe