oWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:710,&quot;width&quot;:835,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:213484,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04d02b44-ebfe-49f7-8976-4a688a78d03f_835x710.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04d02b44-ebfe-49f7-8976-4a688a78d03f_835x710.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04d02b44-ebfe-49f7-8976-4a688a78d03f_835x710.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04d02b44-ebfe-49f7-8976-4a688a78d03f_835x710.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>这是选举季节，因此病毒图表正在迅速而激烈，因为双方都试图支持一种有助于候选人获胜的经济叙事。在这些尝试，陷入困境，动荡的时期，您基本上是一个聪明的新闻消费者。您不能相信任何一个来源 - 甚至我！ - 成为经济趋势和事件的完全公正的解释者。您能做的最好的方法是获取尽可能多的数据，并尝试使用自己的逻辑和理性能力来弄清楚发生了什么。</p><p>但是，即使我不能成为您的单一完美信息来源，我<em>也可以</em>尝试帮助您磨练自己的怀疑，并认识到您何时被喂养的叙述无法坚持。去年9月，我写了一篇有关如何发现误导性病毒图表的文章： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;0219015e-e8a4-4210-b0fa-7187f3d368ac&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&#8220;The art of any propagandist and agitator consists in his ability to find the best means of influencing any given audience, by presenting a definite truth, in such a way as to make it most convincing, most easy to digest, most graphic, and most strongly impressive.&#8221; &#8212; Lenin&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;How not to be fooled by viral charts&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-09-13T01:20:51.010Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9b39106-a033-4d58-9a83-ad16b92bcd89_618x620.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-not-to-be-fooled-by-viral-charts&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:136955075,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:339,&quot;comment_count&quot;:91,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}"></div><p>在我给出的示例中 - 其中包括我在彭博日张贴的图表！ - 图表中的数据要么是不正确的，要么以误导方式呈现。但是，在许多图表中，基础数据可能是牢固的，而数据的呈现显然并不<em>糟糕</em>，但是人们在图表上附加的叙述不是故事的故事，数据确实在说明。 。</p><p>这就是我指南的第2部分的主题，即如何不被病毒图表欺骗。我将通过研究在2010年代末经济辩论中非常受欢迎和影响力的四个图表来说明我的意思：</p><ol><li><p>美国企业学院的“世纪图”</p></li><li><p>经济政策研究所的“生产力与薪酬”图表</p></li><li><p>Lakner＆Milanovic的“大象图”</p></li><li><p>李·德鲁特（Lee Drutman）的“政治指南针”图表</p></li></ol><p>但是首先，只是我在说什么的快速示例。前几天，泰勒·妮可·罗杰斯（Taylor Nicole Rogers）和伊娃肖（Eva Xiao）<a href="https://www.ft.com/content/f0e38c4d-e875-406d-a61b-78cb7c79a4eb">在《金融时报》上写了一个故事</a>，讲述了移民面对婴儿繁荣退休时如何帮助维持美国劳动力的故事。他们用图表说明了这一点： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg" width="815" height="733" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&